---
<MainLayout title="About" description={`Hey! This is the About page.`}>
        <h1 class="font-size-3 title-spacing">About</h1>
        <section>
            <h2 class="font-size-2">Short bio</h2>
            <div class="bio">
                <p>Although he graduated with a degree in film studies, Nikin’s interest in technology and design led
                    him to a career in UX design. From Freshbooks to Say Yeah!, Nikin helped craft interfaces and
                    front-end code that balanced business and user objectives.</p>
                <p>Having spent all his life in Canada, Nikin moved to London, United Kingdom in spring 2019 where he’s
                    now focused on supporting the Government Digital Service as an interaction designer.</p>
                <p>Aside from his day-to-day work, Nikin is an avid photographer, aiming to capture the everyday as
                    cinematic.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="font-size-2">Work</h2>
            <ul class="list-extra-spaced">
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">Government Digital Service</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">London, United
                                Kingdom</span></p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2020-08" class="capitalize">August
                                2020</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">A Million Ads</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">London, United
                                Kingdom</span></p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2019-06" class="capitalize">June
                                2019</time> <span class="visually-hidden">to</span> <time datetime="2020-08"
                                class="dash capitalize">August 2020</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">Say Yeah!</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">Toronto, Canada</span>
                        </p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2019-08" class="capitalize">August
                                2019</time> <span class="visually-hidden">to</span> <time datetime="2019-11"
                                class="dash capitalize">November 2019</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">Freshbooks</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">Toronto, Canada</span>
                        </p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2015-05" class="capitalize">May
                                2015</time> <span class="visually-hidden">to</span> <time datetime="2018-03"
                                class="dash capitalize">March 2018</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="font-size-2">Education</h2>
            <ul class="list-extra-spaced">
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">Juno College of Technology</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">Toronto, Canada</span>
                        </p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2014-09"
                                class="capitalize">September 2014</time> <span class="visually-hidden">to</span> <time
                                datetime="2014-11" class="dash capitalize">November 2014</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3 class="font-size-1">OCAD University</h3>
                    <div class="meta-information">
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">Based in</span> <span class="capitalize">Toronto, Canada</span>
                        </p>
                        <p><span class="visually-hidden">From</span> <time datetime="2011-09"
                                class="capitalize">September 2011</time> <span class="visually-hidden">to</span> <time
                                datetime="2013-06" class="dash capitalize">June 2013</time></p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
